## Bundled AWS Pricing Data

The pricing data files under `pricing-data/` are retrieved from the
AWS Price List API
(https://pricing.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/offers/v1.0/aws/).

This data is provided for informational purposes only and may not
reflect actual charges. AWS pricing is subject to change without notice.

